# UI & Support Rules

## UI Standards

- Framework: Next.js + TailwindCSS.
- Components: Use the shadcn/ui library.
- Ensure the dashboard is responsive and mobile-friendly.

## Support Assistant (Non-AI)

- The Support Assistant is **Rule-Based/FAQ-lookup only**.
- DO NOT implement generative AI or LLM learning for the support module.
- If no match is found, trigger the **Escalation Email** service.
